item.title: Vimy Ridge
item.description: The Battle of Vimy Ridge was part of the Battle of Arras, in the Pas-de-Calais department of France, during the First World War.

item.title: World War II
item.description: In 1939, Germany invaded Poland. This started more than six years of bitter fighting in the Second World War, which finally ended in 1945.
